<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مِنْ ١٢١ - ١٢٩<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فِيهَا ٣ بَنَاتِ لَبُونٍ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مِنْ ١٣٠ - ١٣٩<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
